        <tbody>
          <tr><td>ChapterPlanner</td><td class=3D"center yes">oui</td><td c=
lass=3D"center yes">oui</td><td>logique =E2=80=94 c'est lui qui doit la tra=
duire en plan</td></tr>
          <tr><td>StoryFidelityCritic / Narrative / Causal</td><td class=3D=
"center yes">oui</td><td class=3D"center yes">oui</td><td>via <code>chapter=
sBlock</code> =E2=80=94 actif en FULL uniquement</td></tr>
          <tr><td>PlanNarrativeCritic</td><td class=3D"center no">non</td><=
td class=3D"center yes">oui</td><td>juge l'arc sans conna=C3=AEtre la consi=
gne compl=C3=A8te</td></tr>
          <tr><td>PlanCoherenceCritic</td><td class=3D"center no">non</td><=
td class=3D"center yes">oui</td><td>idem</td></tr>
          <tr><td>GoalPlanCritic</td><td class=3D"center no">non</td><td cl=
ass=3D"center yes">oui</td><td>idem</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Writer</td><td class=3D"center no">non*</td><td class=3D"=
center no">non</td><td>*re=C3=A7oit <code>chapterPlan</code> (d=C3=A9riv=C3=
=A9 de la consigne) + <code>sequence.directive()</code>, pas la consigne br=
ute</td></tr>
          <tr><td>TextNarrativeCritic</td><td class=3D"center no">non</td><=
td class=3D"center no">non</td><td>ne re=C3=A7oit m=C3=AAme pas l'objet <co=
de>Chapter</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td>TextCoherenceCritic</td><td class=3D"center no">non</td><=
td class=3D"center no">non</td><td>re=C3=A7oit <code>Chapter</code> mais n'=
en lit ni goal ni description</td></tr>
          <tr><td>GoalTextCritic</td><td class=3D"center no">non</td><td cl=
ass=3D"center yes">oui</td><td>seul critic de texte correctement branch=C3=
=A9 sur le goal</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id=3D"plan-livre" class=3D"phase">
    <div class=3D"phase-head"><span class=3D"phase-num">Phase 1</span><h2>P=
lan livre</h2></div>
    <p class=3D"phase-desc">Critique globale sur l'ensemble des plans de ch=
apitres concat=C3=A9n=C3=A9s =E2=80=94 active uniquement en qualit=C3=A9 FU=
LL, avant toute =C3=A9criture.</p>

    <div class=3D"agents">
      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">StoryFidelityC=
ritic</span><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">V=C3=A9rifie que chaque plan de chapitre r=C3=A9a=
lise fid=C3=A8lement la consigne de l'auteur (description + objectif), =C3=
=A0 l'=C3=A9chelle du livre entier.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">bookGoal</span><span class=3D"field">chaptersBlock (=
titre + consigne + objectif + plan, par chapitre)</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note ras">Le seul agent de toute la cha=C3=AEne =C3=A0 =
voir consigne et plan ensemble, =C3=A0 l'=C3=A9chelle du livre. Rappel : in=
actif hors qualit=C3=A9 FULL =E2=80=94 c'est un choix de co=C3=BBt document=
=C3=A9, pas un manque de c=C3=A2blage.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">StoryNarrative=
Critic</span><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Rep=C3=A8re les incoh=C3=A9rences d'arc de person=
nage entre les ajouts (au-del=C3=A0 de la consigne) de deux chapitres diff=
=C3=A9rents.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">bookGoal</span><span class=3D"field">chaptersBlock</=
span></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note ras">Entr=C3=A9es coh=C3=A9rentes avec un r=C3=B4l=
e explicitement born=C3=A9 aux =C2=AB ajouts de l'IA =C2=BB =E2=80=94 ne ju=
ge jamais la consigne elle-m=C3=AAme.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">StoryCausalCri=
tic</span><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Rep=C3=A8re les contradictions factuelles entre l=
es ajouts (au-del=C3=A0 de la consigne) de deux chapitres diff=C3=A9rents.<=
/p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">bookGoal</span><span class=3D"field">chaptersBlock</=
span></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note ras">M=C3=AAme remarque que StoryNarrativeCritic. =
Les trois critics livre ne comparent les chapitres qu'entre eux, jamais con=
tre les fiches lore/personnages =E2=80=94 coh=C3=A9rent avec leur d=C3=A9fi=
nition (=C2=AB ajout de l'IA contredit un autre ajout de l'IA =C2=BB), pas =
un manque.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id=3D"plan-chapitre" class=3D"phase">
    <div class=3D"phase-head"><span class=3D"phase-num">Phase 2</span><h2>P=
lan chapitre</h2></div>
    <p class=3D"phase-desc">G=C3=A9n=C3=A9ration puis critique du plan d'un=
 chapitre =E2=80=94 beats par s=C3=A9quence, coh=C3=A9rence, arc narratif, =
atteinte de l'objectif.</p>

    <div class=3D"agents">
      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">ChapterPlanner=
</span><span class=3D"verdict bad">Anomalie</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Produit le plan d'un chapitre =E2=80=94 libre ou =
JSON structur=C3=A9 par s=C3=A9quence (beats, sensoriels, intention de sc=
=C3=A8ne).</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
>
            <span class=3D"field">chapterTitle</span><span class=3D"field">=
chapterDescription</span><span class=3D"field">chapterSetting</span>
            <span class=3D"field">sequenceDescriptions (+ beats hint)</span=
><span class=3D"field">bookGoal</span><span class=3D"field">storySoFar</spa=
n>
            <span class=3D"field">entityState</span><span class=3D"field">c=
haracters (chapitre)</span><span class=3D"field">constraints</span>
            <span class=3D"field">focusText / loreText (chapitre)</span><sp=
an class=3D"field">coherence</span><span class=3D"field">forbiddenPhrases</=
span>
            <span class=3D"field">isRewrite / previousPlan</span><span clas=
s=3D"field">problemsToFix</span>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note bad"><strong>coherence</strong> et <strong>problem=
sToFix</strong> re=C3=A7oivent la m=C3=AAme cha=C3=AEne (<code>wc.coherence=
()</code>), affich=C3=A9e sous deux titres diff=C3=A9rents ("=C3=89tat de c=
oh=C3=A9rence" / "Probl=C3=A8mes =C3=A0 corriger imp=C3=A9rativement"). Pro=
position : soit supprimer un des deux champs, soit leur donner un contenu r=
=C3=A9ellement distinct si la duplication n'=C3=A9tait pas voulue.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">PlanNarrativeC=
ritic</span><span class=3D"verdict warn">=C3=80 enrichir</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">=C3=89value la progression de l'arc narratif d'un=
 plan de chapitre.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">plan</span><span class=3D"field">bookGoal</span><spa=
n class=3D"field">chapterGoal</span></div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Absent, potentiellement utile</h5><div c=
lass=3D"fieldlist">
            <span class=3D"field missing">chapterDescription</span><span cl=
ass=3D"field missing">characters</span><span class=3D"field missing">storyS=
oFar</span>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note warn">Sans la consigne (<code>chapterDescription</=
code>), l'agent peut qualifier de "d=C3=A9faut d'arc" un choix que l'auteur=
 a explicitement demand=C3=A9 mais qui n'appara=C3=AEt pas dans le <code>go=
al</code> court. Proposition : ajouter <code>chapterDescription</code>, pr=
=C3=A9sent=C3=A9e avant le plan (m=C3=AAme ordre que StoryFidelityCritic).<=
/p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">PlanCoherenceC=
ritic</span><span class=3D"verdict warn">=C3=80 enrichir</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">V=C3=A9rifie la coh=C3=A9rence factuelle d'un pla=
n (fiches personnages, contraintes, continuit=C3=A9 intra-plan).</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
>
            <span class=3D"field">enrichedPlan (+ points_a_verifier/focus/l=
ore par s=C3=A9quence)</span><span class=3D"field">chapterGoal</span>
            <span class=3D"field">checks (sc=C3=A9nario + chapitre)</span><=
span class=3D"field">characters (fusion chapitre + s=C3=A9quences)</span>
          </div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Absent, potentiellement utile</h5><div c=
lass=3D"fieldlist">
            <span class=3D"field missing">chapterDescription</span><span cl=
ass=3D"field missing">entityState</span>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note warn">Le prompt sait d=C3=A9j=C3=A0 chercher des c=
ontradictions type =C2=AB fiche dit 1943, le plan dit 1942 =C2=BB =E2=80=94=
 mais seulement entre s=C3=A9quences du m=C3=AAme plan, faute d'acc=C3=A8s =
=C3=A0 <code>entityState</code> (faits d=C3=A9j=C3=A0 =C3=A9tablis par les =
chapitres pr=C3=A9c=C3=A9dents). Un plan qui contredit un fait d=C3=A9j=C3=
=A0 pos=C3=A9 dans l'histoire passera inaper=C3=A7u ici tant que le critic =
livre (FULL uniquement) ne tourne pas.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">GoalPlanCritic=
</span><span class=3D"verdict warn">=C3=80 enrichir</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">V=C3=A9rifie que le plan fait avancer concr=C3=A8=
tement l'objectif narratif du chapitre.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">plan</span><span class=3D"field">chapterGoal</span><=
span class=3D"field">bookGoal</span></div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Absent, potentiellement utile</h5><div c=
lass=3D"fieldlist"><span class=3D"field missing">chapterDescription</span><=
/div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note warn">M=C3=AAme remarque que PlanNarrativeCritic :=
 le <code>goal</code> seul peut =C3=AAtre trop court pour juger si le plan =
"avance vers" ce que l'auteur attend r=C3=A9ellement de ce chapitre.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id=3D"write-writer" class=3D"phase">
    <div class=3D"phase-head"><span class=3D"phase-num">Phase 3</span><h2>W=
rite s=C3=A9quence =E2=80=94 Writer &amp; correcteurs</h2></div>
    <p class=3D"phase-desc">R=C3=A9daction d'une s=C3=A9quence, puis quatre=
 passes de correction inline (patches FAUX=E2=86=92JUSTE appliqu=C3=A9s en =
Java, jamais de r=C3=A9=C3=A9criture directe par le LLM).</p>

    <div class=3D"agents">
      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">Writer</span><=
span class=3D"verdict warn">Champs morts</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">R=C3=A9dige la prose d'une s=C3=A9quence =C3=A0 p=
artir de la trame, des directives et du contexte narratif accumul=C3=A9.</p=
>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
>
            <span class=3D"field">sequenceDescription / sequencePlan</span>=
<span class=3D"field">minWords</span><span class=3D"field">isRewrite</span>
            <span class=3D"field">charactersText (chapitre+s=C3=A9quence)</=
span><span class=3D"field">focusText / loreText (chapitre+s=C3=A9quence)</s=
pan>
            <span class=3D"field">chapterPlan (+ probl=C3=A8mes si r=C3=A9=
=C3=A9criture)</span><span class=3D"field">prevSentences</span><span class=
=3D"field">entityState</span>
            <span class=3D"field">storySoFar</span><span class=3D"field">fo=
rbiddenPhrases / forbiddenThemes</span><span class=3D"field">redactionConst=
raints</span>
            <span class=3D"field">writingExample</span><span class=3D"field=
">setting</span><span class=3D"field">stitch</span>
          </div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Toujours nul ou vide (c=C3=A2blage jamai=
s branch=C3=A9)</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist">
            <span class=3D"field missing">loopJournal (null)</span><span cl=
ass=3D"field missing">styleGuide (null)</span>
            <span class=3D"field missing">sequenceContext (null)</span><spa=
n class=3D"field missing">actionsText ("")</span>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note warn">L'agent le mieux nourri de la cha=C3=AEne =
=E2=80=94 =C3=A0 raison, c'est lui qui =C3=A9crit. Mais 4 champs pr=C3=A9vu=
s dans <code>WriterInput</code> et g=C3=A9r=C3=A9s dans <code>buildUser()</=
code> ne sont jamais aliment=C3=A9s par <code>WriterStep</code>. Le plus co=
ncret : <code>styleGuide</code> pourrait porter <code>scenario.writingStyle=
()</code> (<code>style.md</code>), aujourd'hui orphelin dans tout le projet=
. D=C3=A9cider consciemment de brancher ou de retirer, plut=C3=B4t que lais=
ser du code mort.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">DeusInMachinaC=
orrector</span><span class=3D"verdict bad">Anomalie</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Corrige en ligne les passages o=C3=B9 la m=C3=A9c=
anique de fabrication devient visible (fuites d'instructions, =C3=A9tiquett=
es de personnage, artefacts de sc=C3=A9nario=E2=80=A6).</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">text</span><span class=3D"field">checks (sc=C3=A9nar=
io + chapitre, pas s=C3=A9quence)</span></div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>R=C3=A9clam=C3=A9 par son propre prompt,=
 jamais fourni</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"><span class=3D"field missing">c=
onsigne de s=C3=A9quence</span><span class=3D"field missing">plan de s=C3=
=A9quence</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note bad">Le SYSTEM prompt dit explicitement de lire en=
 priorit=C3=A9 la consigne/le plan de s=C3=A9quence pour ne pas corriger =
=C3=A0 tort un passage voulu =E2=80=94 mais ni l'un ni l'autre n'existe dan=
s <code>DeusInMachinaCorrectorInput</code>. Risque concret : correction err=
on=C3=A9e d'un passage qui r=C3=A9alisait fid=C3=A8lement la directive de l=
a s=C3=A9quence, faute de moyen de le savoir. Ajouter <code>sequence.direct=
ive()</code> (et le plan de s=C3=A9quence s'il existe) r=C3=A9soudrait =C3=
=A0 la fois ce trou et l'incoh=C3=A9rence documentaire.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">NaturalityCorr=
ector</span><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Corrige les formulations artificielles, surconstr=
uites ou analytiques ("ambiance expliqu=C3=A9e", "conclusions narratorielle=
s"=E2=80=A6).</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid"><div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5>=
<div class=3D"fieldlist"><span class=3D"field">text</span></div></div></div=
>
        <p class=3D"note ras">T=C3=A2che purement stylistique et ind=C3=A9p=
endante du contenu =E2=80=94 aucun contexte sc=C3=A9nario n=C3=A9cessaire p=
our la remplir correctement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">StyleCorrector=
</span><span class=3D"verdict bad">Anomalie</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Corrige les faiblesses de style (verbes faibles, =
r=C3=A9p=C3=A9titions de structure, clich=C3=A9s, transitions m=C3=A9caniqu=
es).</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">text</span><span class=3D"field">writingExample</spa=
n></div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Toujours nul</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist=
"><span class=3D"field missing">styleGuide</span><span class=3D"field missi=
ng">qualityCriteria</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note bad"><code>StyleCorrectorStep</code> instancie <co=
de>new StyleCorrectorInput(text, null, null, scenario.writingExample())</co=
de>. Pourtant <code>StyleCorrector.buildSystem()</code> contient une branch=
e <code>hasStyle</code> enti=C3=A8rement d=C3=A9di=C3=A9e =C3=A0 exploiter =
un guide de style s'il est pr=C3=A9sent. <code>scenario.writingStyle()</cod=
e> (<code>style.md</code>) et <code>scenario.quality()</code> (<code>qualit=
y.md</code>) sont charg=C3=A9s depuis le disque mais n'alimentent jamais ce=
t agent =E2=80=94 ni aucun autre agent actif du projet.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">ProofreaderCor=
rector</span><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">Corrige grammaire, orthographe, accords, syntaxe.=
</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid"><div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5>=
<div class=3D"fieldlist"><span class=3D"field">text</span></div></div></div=
>
        <p class=3D"note ras">T=C3=A2che ind=C3=A9pendante du contenu narra=
tif =E2=80=94 p=C3=A9rim=C3=A8tre minimal correct.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id=3D"write-critiques" class=3D"phase">
    <div class=3D"phase-head"><span class=3D"phase-num">Phase 3 (suite)</sp=
an><h2>Write s=C3=A9quence =E2=80=94 critiques</h2></div>
    <p class=3D"phase-desc">Critique globale lanc=C3=A9e apr=C3=A8s les cor=
recteurs =E2=80=94 score moyen, retour au Writer si sous le seuil.</p>

    <div class=3D"agents">
      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">DeusInMachinaC=
ritic</span><span class=3D"verdict bad">Anomalie</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">D=C3=A9tecte (sans corriger) les m=C3=AAmes cinq =
types de fuites que son homologue Corrector.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid">
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"=
><span class=3D"field">text</span><span class=3D"field">checks (sc=C3=A9nar=
io + chapitre, pas s=C3=A9quence)</span></div></div>
          <div class=3D"block"><h5>R=C3=A9clam=C3=A9 par son propre prompt,=
 jamais fourni</h5><div class=3D"fieldlist"><span class=3D"field missing">c=
onsigne de s=C3=A9quence</span><span class=3D"field missing">plan de s=C3=
=A9quence</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class=3D"note bad">M=C3=AAme anomalie exacte que DeusInMachinaCo=
rrector =E2=80=94 les deux agents partagent le m=C3=AAme SYSTEM en t=C3=AAt=
e de prompt et le m=C3=AAme trou de donn=C3=A9es. =C3=80 corriger ensemble.=
</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">PlanFidelityCr=
itic</span><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">V=C3=A9rifie que chaque beat planifi=C3=A9 pour l=
a s=C3=A9quence est bien d=C3=A9velopp=C3=A9 dans le texte r=C3=A9dig=C3=A9=
.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid"><div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5>=
<div class=3D"fieldlist"><span class=3D"field">beats (extraits du plan de s=
=C3=A9quence)</span><span class=3D"field">sequenceText</span></div></div></=
div>
        <p class=3D"note ras">P=C3=A9rim=C3=A8tre minimal et exact pour sa =
t=C3=A2che =E2=80=94 rien =C3=A0 ajouter, rien =C3=A0 enlever.</p>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"agent">
        <div class=3D"agent-head"><span class=3D"agent-name">CheckCritic</s=
pan><span class=3D"verdict ok">RAS</span></div>
        <p class=3D"role">V=C3=A9rifie que chaque point de contr=C3=B4le d=
=C3=A9clar=C3=A9 dans le sc=C3=A9nario est respect=C3=A9 dans le texte.</p>
        <div class=3D"agent-grid"><div class=3D"block"><h5>Re=C3=A7oit</h5>=
